Poetry for participating in Men's Day celebration
Topic: Childhood
Name: SHUBHAM KUCHERIA
Emp Id: 03725
Dept: PDT1


kuch nanhi barish ki boondo ki tarah,
gujar gya tha bachpana,

khel , kood, bhag daud me hi tha,
hasrat ka poora hona,

nachte, gaate, yaro se milna,
ladkar bhi maan jaana,

bane huye ko bigaad dena aur rutho ko bhi mana lena,

gande kapde , gandi galiya per iski kisko chinta,

khilono k liye zid karna aur na milne per rona,

vo mitti se mahal banana aur khud ko sartaz samajhna,

apne hi khayalo me rehna aur rat k sitaro me khud ko aasman me dekhna,

hath me khilone aur aankho me sapne,

nanhe hatho se apne hi kal ko bunn lena,

kisi ki ak baat na sunna,
rona , chillana magar gudgudi karne per jor se muskurana,

jhoolo pe uper jaana , fisal patti se niche,
uthna , girna aur fir se sambhalna,

maa ki god me chain ki neend,
pita k sath sahas k kadam badhana,

bhai behan ka sath nok-jhok,
aur har khushi-dukh me apno ko sath hona,

anjaano se bhi apnapan samajhna ,
aur dusro ki khushi me khud ki hi khushi samajhna,

ak patang ban k udd jana, hawa k sath behte jana,

bas aise hi masti bhare din gujarte jana,

 vo din nhi hai ab ye maine maana,
 kash vo din fir laut aaye ,
mujhe hai fir se mere bachpan me jana.
